{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"lb13v51ovudumswv6n3tgrd","title":"customer-insight-through-IDIs","desc":"","updated":1663991883754,"created":1663985699277,"custom":{},"fname":"marketing.customer-insight-through-IDIs","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"be5d1575152583b6c275a9c0da4abbe3","links":[],"anchors":{"customer-insight-through-idis---marketing-research":{"type":"header","text":"Customer Insight through IDIs - Marketing Research","value":"customer-insight-through-idis---marketing-research","line":12,"column":0,"depth":1},"definitions":{"type":"header","text":"Definitions","value":"definitions","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"question":{"type":"header","text":"Question","value":"question","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"customer-insight-through-idis\">customer-insight-through-IDIs<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#customer-insight-through-idis\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#customer-insight-through-idis---marketing-research\">Customer Insight through IDIs - Marketing Research</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#definitions\">Definitions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#question\">Question</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"customer-insight-through-idis---marketing-research\">Customer Insight through IDIs - Marketing Research<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#customer-insight-through-idis---marketing-research\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"definitions\">Definitions<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#definitions\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>IDIs: In-depth Interviews\n<ul>\n<li>conducting intensive interviewers with a number of respondents to explore their perspective</li>\n<li>=> group interviews, n interviewers - m respondents</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Marketing Research:\n<ul>\n<li>Primary Research methods\n<ul>\n<li>Interviews</li>\n<li>Surveys</li>\n<li>Primary vs Secondary (desk research) researchs  </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"question\">Question<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#question\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In-depth Interviews why &#x26; who:\n<ul>\n<li>small sample size</li>\n<li>selective individuals</li>\n<li><strong>valuable knowledge => Professional interview</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Private interview => sensitive information => Need agreement</strong></li>\n<li>Personalize data</li>\n<li><strong>Difficulty to interview in a group</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Where?\n<ul>\n<li>Interviewee preference\n<ul>\n<li>Schedule compatible</li>\n<li><strong>Comfortable</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>How long?\n<ul>\n<li>&#x3C;= 1 hours (45-60 mins) -> build questions</li>\n<li>Agreements</li>\n<li>&#x3C; require time\n<ul>\n<li>Shrink time</li>\n<li>move schedule (not recommend) -> to another day</li>\n<li>Shift schedule (mins-hours) -> in day</li>\n<li>Handle\n<ul>\n<li>questions preview send to interviewee</li>\n<li>Ask high priority questions      </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8